<br>
Do a search over at Steel Warriors or The Safehouse.  You'll probably find lots of contradictions.<br>
<br>
The things I've heard which may or may not be true:<br>
<br>
- Haste cap varies with level, up to 100% at Lv60.<br>
- You cannot swing a weapon more than once a second (ie haste never drops delay below 10 even if the calcs say it should).<br>
- There are three things that stack with haste - item haste, spell haste and song haste.  Some songs allow you to exceed the cap (if it exists).<br>
<br>
Hope that helps some.<br>
